title: Woohooo! Stable Release!
description: First fully stable release after experimental versions. Website launched and icons library working like expected.

title: Corrected misspelled component
description: Fixed typo in Calendar icon component names (previously 'Calender' and 'CalenderAlt', now 'Calendar' and 'CalendarAlt'). Updated import paths to use correct spelling.

title: 12 New Icons Added!
description: Added 12 new icons to the library: CheckMark, CoffeeMug, Cross, Home, LightBulb, and Web (each with Alt variants). Library now includes 52 icons total.
